window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Ever wonder what a prison riot is like? </p> <p>B.J., a white inmate serving time on drug charges, gets caught up in a Mexican gang war. The northern California Mexicans demand that the southern California Mexicans keep their shirts on to cover up their gangland tattoos. The prison explodes into chaos as each building erupts in deadly violence. </p> <p>For B.J, the war isn't over when he and over a hundred inmates get housed in solitary confinement, it's just beginning. For getting involved, he's labeled a southern Mexican gangster. </p> <p>The hardcore action unfolds like a movie in this bare bones thriller of true crime.</p>"; 
